---
Show accumulated session warnings

Usage: tirith warnings [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --clear              Clear session warnings after display
      --session <SESSION>  Override session ID
      --format <FORMAT>    Output format (default: human) [possible values: human, json]
      --summary            One-line summary (for shell exit hooks)
      --hidden             Show findings hidden by paranoia filtering
  -h, --help               Print help

Examples:
  tirith warnings
  tirith warnings --format json
  tirith warnings --hidden
